description:
Use <U+2060>parse_*()<U+2060> if you have a character vector you want to parse. Use
<U+2060>col_*()<U+2060> in conjunction with a <U+2060>read_*()<U+2060> function to parse the
values as they're read in.
example_call: parse_character(x, na = c("", "NA"), locale = default_locale(), trim_ws = TRUE)
